org.conqat.engine.service.shared.client

Interface ServiceClientCallable<T>

  • Functional Interface:
    This is a functional interface and can therefore be used as the assignment target for a lambda expression or method reference.

    @FunctionalInterface
public interface ServiceClientCallable<T>
    Interface to enable testing service calls with provided responses. For an example see IdeServiceClientTest.
